          "description": "<span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249);\">### 九域来历 (世界观) 世界树（众生之母）：混沌海的第一个生灵，因为寂寞创造了无数世界和生灵，但是都被混沌海化为虚无，最终化身为世界树树根插入混沌海吸收虚无之力转化为催生世界的力量，托起世界果远离混沌海。世界树不断壮大，世界果越结越多但是吸收虚无之力过多让世界树无法维持转换，引起了混沌力量的反噬，世界果突然大规模崩坏。 世界树被混沌海冲刷崩坏，世界树的所有世界被虚无破灭，世界树核心太初莲（世界树意志）沉入混沌海，九瓣莲花是最后九个世界。太初莲的知道无论多少纪元自己迟早破灭，于是设计主动崩坏自己的意识核心定界珠，让虚无冲击9个世界，定界珠碎片可以帮助稳定9界不被虚无破灭，但是无法避免虚无的冲刷，虚无冲刷世界会在世界中形成投影是为天魔。</span><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: collapse;\"><br></div><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: collapse;\">9个世界在世界土著哪里被称为9重天，上三天拥有最大的定界珠碎片，最为稳定受到的冲刷最小，被称为仙界。</div><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: collapse;\">中三天，受到上三天的保护和管理，被下三天和天魔攻击，称为凡界。下三天因为只有少量定界珠碎片，很多地方已经被侵蚀，被侵蚀的地方成为深渊总有大量天魔从深渊出现，也被称为魔界。</div><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: collapse;\"><br></div><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: collapse;\">9重天围绕着破碎的定界珠旋转，有时花瓣会相互穿过，界域交互之时就会出现界域通道引发界域入侵现象。</div><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: collapse;\">上三天</div><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: collapse;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">玉清天·太上道庭</strong></div><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: collapse;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-siz